    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A yuri horror visual novel inspired by Azores folklore.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/271e3554ef574fdca9dccdfcacda1cc4.avif?t=1771952414\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Margo Silva has done everything she can to leave behind the trailer park in Arizona where she grew up. Now all she has to do is focus on her summer job until she can leave for college. Her illusion of a quiet summer is shattered when a hungry ghost enters her dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two mysterious girls show up in town, claiming they can help her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Margo must contend with a demon's claim on her soul, and how to stop ghosts from this life and the past that want to take her future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/7be63f7c42cf9437e910c39f4983d251.avif?t=1771952414\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/ced09c54aebc7a67d09413dc297b2cc1.avif?t=1771952414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras_big/ced09c54aebc7a67d09413dc297b2cc1.avif?t=1771952414 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/69e1d098652dc03d44771889075306ea.avif?t=1771952414\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras_big/69e1d098652dc03d44771889075306ea.avif?t=1771952414 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/361cac6857ca5070f23e614b3933ff37.avif?t=1771952414\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEMO</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Demo may not reflect all updates that are in Early Access.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 2 hours of gameplay and reading.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game story spanning June 7th to June 20th.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EARLY ACCESS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Early Access version is in active development and may change.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 13 hours of gameplay and reading.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive story with player choice for conversations, relationships, and actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200+ choices.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story is structured so that the player experiences each individual day of the summer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game story spanning June 7th to August 16th.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 unlockable gallery images.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 sapphic romance routes, based on your decisions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack inspired by 90's alternative.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original retro inspired dithered art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partial voice acting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FULL GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Full Game features may change, these are estimates.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 20 hours of gameplay and reading.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 200k words.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game story spanning June 7th to September 1st.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 gallery images.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 sapphic romance routes, 1 secret route.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/2adacd4bab87782e08eeb1b3ce6099af.poster.avif?t=1771952414\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/2adacd4bab87782e08eeb1b3ce6099af.webm?t=1771952414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271270/extras/2adacd4bab87782e08eeb1b3ce6099af.mp4?t=1771952414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
